How can I setup my Paypal account to receive payments ?

The Problem :
I try to transfer money from my Upwork account to my Paypal but it refuses ... I asked Upwork and they say "I have checked on this and it seems Paypal has been rejecting funds coming from Upwork. I suggest that you contact Paypal Support to clarify the issue from their end "

My Trials : I have tried to send payments many times but .. noway.
I have setup Paypal account and says it's "Your Profile is at 100%" tried sending again but still not working.

Please have you faced this problem before ? and how to fix it ?

حقك تعمل نقابة, واحتكر أى لقب (مهندس برمجيات أو غيره ), معندناش أى مشكلة, لكن أنت مش واصى عليا, آخد تصريح منك (وأدفع لحضرتك أرضيه/إتاوه)علشان تسيبنى أشتغل, وفى النهاية مليش أى حق أعترض على أى قرار أصدرته النقابة, أو حتى أشارك فى إتجاهاتها وقرارتها.
